          <p>Hidden Hook is your source for premium flies. Every fly that leaves our shop is spun with top-of-the-line materials and components. At Hidden Hook we take pride in each fly that leaves the vice and guarantee their flawless performance. Each fly is hand tied by Hidden Hook founder Rudy Babikian.   </p>
